column17: either using a search engine or via social media

I have my history and recomendations disabled all the time, this leaves me with two options for finding information and videos on youtube: 1. through my subscribed creators, 2. by searching in the YouTube search engine. In the context of information itself I typically use large youtube creators that process information, this allows me to stay informed without spending too much time on searching individual keywords.
